These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, turquise
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
City: nizza, boston
1. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Color       | turquise       | lilac |
| Movie-Genre         | crime | action  |
| Beverage       | iced-tea    | almond-milk    |
| City   | boston       | nizza      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, punk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, november
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, red
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, polish
1. the person who likes azure is on the right of the nigerian##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes azure is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Music-Genre      | punk     | ambient |
| Birthday           | may | november      |
| Color   | red  | azure      |
| Nationality         | nigerian | polish     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
House: cottage, farmhouse
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, polish
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, prince
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, dahlia
1. the prince-smoker is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the cottage house is the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the pakistani is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| House      | cottage | farmhouse  |
| Nationality          | pakistani    | polish   |
| Cigar   | prince  | bongani   |
| Flower     | dahlia     | balloon-flower |

