.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, canasta
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, magic-tricks
House: colonial, ranch-style
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, basketball
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
2. the colonial house is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing canasta is the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Game      | scrabble       | canasta |
| Hobby          | magic-tricks         | video-games    |
| House           | ranch-style | colonial    |
| Sport   | golf           | basketball   |

