.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, december
2 different games are played: whist, monopoly
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, prince
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Birthday           | december | august     |
| Game   | whist          | monopoly |
| Beverage           | coffee          | almond-milk    |
| Cigar     | prince            | dunhill       |

 